Scope of this license

This MIT license covers the CODE and DOCUMENTATION in this repository only.

It does NOT grant any rights to the underlying data, which are not distributed
here and are governed by separate agreements (see data/DATA_ACCESS.md):

  * Alabama Department of Human Resources (DHR) administrative child care
    licensing records and quarterly provider surveys, obtained by the
    University of Alabama under a one-way Data Transfer and Use Agreement
    (Agreement A24-0563) and confidential under Ala. Code § 38-2-6.

  * Commercial rooftop geocoding of provider addresses, licensed from Melissa
    (www.melissa.com) for one-time use and not redistributable.

The published aggregate results shipped here -- the figures, tables, the tract-
and county-level result files under data/derived/, and the scalar registry
key_numbers.csv -- are derived, disclosure-safe summaries released with the
accompanying paper. They contain no provider coordinates and no individual or
record-level values; small cells are suppressed. See data/DATA_ACCESS.md for
the full data-governance statement.
